cated. If tests exercise Activator/OsgiRegistry, use in-memory OSGi Bundle/BundleContext test doubles and implement the OSGi 4.2 Bundle methods required by org.osgi.core 4.2.0.\",\n  \"risks\": [\n    \"Keeping org.osgi:osgi_R4_core:1.0 alongside org.osgi:org.osgi.core:4.2.0 can create duplicate org.osgi.framework classes; local Gradle verification should confirm classpath behavior.\"\n  ]\n}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0c5777dc05351604016a430e1d7d6c819492cce5cb99374fd4\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 2622, "output": 1332, "cacheRead": 26112, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 30066, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782779400855, "responseId": "resp_0c5777dc05351604016a430e095e808194b193ad5e11913b56"}, "toolResults": []}
